            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日（10 月 1 日）中國慶祝成立 75 週年，中國深圳一連 7 日舉行「天空之城大有可能」無人機表演，逾萬架無人機在夜空進行燈光表演，吸引了大量當地民眾觀賞，龍崗、福田、羅湖、龍華及大鵬，都有無人機正常表演。同日香港舉辦的「中國國慶煙花匯演」亦首次加入無人機環節，但據悉因「電離層閃爍」影響無人機接收衞星定位訊號，最終表演告吹。無獨有偶，香港原定於 9 月 30 日晚在維多利亞港上空舉行「新生代千人合唱賀國慶」無人機表演，亦疑因太陽風暴幹擾而取消。連同上月 21 日嗇色園聯同黃大仙民政事務處舉辦的《黃大仙寶誕·紫氣龍騰耀香江—無人機匯演》，香港近期已經有 3 次同類型無人機表演臨場取消。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130225.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p>昨日（10 月 1 日）中國深圳如期舉行無人機表演，無人機排列出巨龍、無人機、AI 晶片、中國深圳天際線等等圖案，成為當地慶祝活動焦點。此次「天空之城大有可能」無人機表演將會結合深圳各個城市特色，由 10 月 1 日至 7 日每日在深圳 5 個地方空中演出。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125626.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍崗以無人機排列出巨龍圖案，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125607.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍崗以無人機排列出無人機圖案，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125538.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍崗亦以無人機排列出 AI 晶片圖案，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002125236.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳福田的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002130311.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳福田以無人機排列出天際線，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266964" src="https://cdn.un