mage-1266976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳羅湖的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131201.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳羅湖的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131242.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳羅湖的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131434.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266980" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131355.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266981" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131603.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華以無人機排列成巨龍形狀，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266982" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131551.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131542.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131453.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳龍華的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1266987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241002131840.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中國深圳大鵬的無人機表演，圖片來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a></p><p>相比之下，香港原定於同日（10 月 1 日）在維港上空舉行煙花匯演，另外亦是首次加插無人機飛行表演環節，惟康文署在當日晚上燃放煙花前宣佈因維港上空出現「電離層閃爍」（ionospheric scintillation）現象而取消無人機環節目。</p><p>據《香港電台》引述天文台指，全球定位系統（Global Positioning System，GPS）無線電訊號需經過電離層傳送訊息至地面接收站，以測量位置提供導航。如太陽活動強烈或會影響並幹擾電離層，令測量位置訊息準確度下降。「電離層閃爍」是無線電波沿著訊號路徑因電離層中電子密度的小尺度結構而產生的快速變化，嚴重情況下會影響 GPS 收發器鎖定訊號，因此 10 月 1 日當天須取消煙花前的無人機表演環節。</p><p>香港 9 月 30 日的「新生代千人合唱賀國慶」無人機表演亦因「受到幹擾出現故障」而取消，據大會表示，事件並不涉及人為幹擾。天文台前助理台長、氣象學會發言人梁榮武在《商業電台》節目表示，太陽風暴引起的電磁擾動，會影響地球磁場，精密儀器或會受到影響，影響飛行安全。</p><p>對於「新生代千人合唱賀國慶」取消無人機飛行一事，《獨立媒體》引述梁榮武指對安排感到「小小奇怪」。梁榮武指，太陽風暴一般影響鄰近南北極的地區，香港位處北緯 21 度南方，如果受到影響的話，相信今次太陽風暴非常強烈。雖然梁榮武認為威脅不大，但由於無人機表演涉及各種不同人因素，其形容大會取消表演是「風險管理」。</p><p>香港無人機表演取消後，市民反應不一。有些人對此感到失望，因為無法看到期待已久的燈光展示；但也有市民認為這是出於安全考量的正確決定。無人機在受幹擾情況下可能無法正常飛行，存在潛在風險，取消活動是避免事故的必要措施。翻查紀錄，今次已是近期第 3 次無人機飛行表演在無預警狀態下取消。對上一次則是由嗇色園聯同黃大仙民政事務處舉辦的《黃大仙寶誕·紫氣龍騰耀香江—無人機匯演》，原定於 9 月 21 日在灣仔海濱維港上空舉行，及後因天雨影響而在原定表演開始時間一小時後臨時宣佈取消。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://weibo.com/l/wblive/p/show/1022:2321325084756697284761">微博直播</a>、<a href="https://www.i-cable.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/275274/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E9%81%87%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%A2%81%E6%A6%AE%E6%AD%A6-%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E6%94%B9">i-Cable</a>、<a href="https://www.881903.com/news/local/2550272/%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%96%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F">商業電台</a>、<a href="https://www.singtaousa.com/2024-10-01/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B675%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%EF%B8%B1%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B37%E5%A4%A95%E5%8D%80%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94-%E5%A4%9C%E7%A9%BA%E5%B7%A8%E9%BE%8D%E7%82%BA/5010349">星島</a>、<a href="https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E9%81%87%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E5%A0%B4-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E6%A2%81%E6%A6%AE%E6%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86">獨立媒體</a>、<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/1062102/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6-2099%E6%9E%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E9%81%87%E5%B9%B2%E6%93%BE%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE-%E4%BF%BE%E4%BD%A0%E6%94%BE%E5%92%97%E5%85%A9%E6%AC%A1%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F">HK01</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1772986-20241002.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f%e8%a1%a8%e6%bc%94-7-7-%e8%b3%80-anson-lo-%e7%94%9f%e6%97%a5-%e6%ad%b7%e6%99%82-12-%e5%88%86%e9%90%98-%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%85%8d%e8%b2%bb%e6%b8%a1%e8%bc%aa/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">無人機表演 7.7 賀 Anson Lo 生日，歷時 12 分鐘 + 提供免費渡輪</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/02/1-october-drones-performance-cancelled/life-tech/drone/">深圳 10.1 五個區無人機表演如常　香港無人機演出三度「放飛機」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
